Class ExternalReferenceProperties

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.accessservices.datamanager.properties.ExternalReferenceProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExternalReferenceRequestBody
public class ExternalReferenceProperties extends Object implements Serializable
ExternalReferenceProperties stores information about an link to an external resource that is relevant to an Asset.
